OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779905470
OL,3,C'Absolute turmoil': Liverpool fan
OL,4,Crebuilding life after attack at Paris
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports Correspondent
OL,8,FElaine Wilcox spoke to Danny in
OL,9,FCrosby, four years after the event.
OL,11,FA Liverpool fan is rebuilding his life
OL,12,Fafter he was severely injured at the
OL,13,FChampions League Final in Paris in
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,FDanny Smith, 51, was with his teenage
OL,17,Fson outside the Stade de France when a
OL,18,Fgang attacked him with a hammer,
OL,19,Fleaving him with potentially life
OL,20,Fchanging wounds to his leg.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
