PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779905470
OL,3,C'Absolute turmoil': Liverpool fan
OL,4,Crebuilding life after attack at Paris
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FHe said: "We were having a lovely time
OL,8,Fat the fan park, all the families, it
OL,9,Fwas a proper carnival atmosphere and
OL,10,Fthen we travelled to St Denis.
OL,12,FDanny said: "We got there and people
OL,13,Fwere being sprayed with pepper spray
OL,14,Fthrough the fence, men, women and
OL,15,Fchildren. It was absolute turmoil."
OL,17,FChaos outside the ground at the 2022
OL,18,Ffinal between Liverpool and Real
OL,19,FMadrid saw supporters with tickets
OL,20,Fmade to wait in huge queues until
OL,21,Fafter the match began.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
