OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779905470
OL,3,C'Absolute turmoil': Liverpool fan
OL,4,Crebuilding life after attack at Paris
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FDanny survived the Hillsborough
OL,8,FDisaster when he was a teenager.
OL,10,FHe said: "It brought me back to being
OL,11,Fa 14-year-old lad again. With the
OL,12,Ftrauma and the crushing physically and
OL,13,Feverything, a lot of people were
OL,14,Ftraumatising from it."
OL,16,FThere were concerns Danny may lose his
OL,17,Fleg due to his injuries, however NHS
OL,18,Fsurgery and then physiotherapy paid
OL,19,Ffor by Liverpool FC has allowed him to
OL,20,Fwalk again.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779905470
OL,3,C'Absolute turmoil': Liverpool fan
OL,4,Crebuilding life after attack at Paris
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,F"There were days I didn't want to get
OL,8,Fout of bed. There were days I didn't
OL,9,Fwant to get up and go to physio, I
OL,10,Fwanted to feel sorry for myself.
OL,12,F"But this wave of support I had - you
OL,13,Fwould let yourself down but you don't
OL,14,Fwant to let other people down."
OL,16,FDanny lost his job due to the damage
OL,17,Fdone to his leg, and he still waiting
OL,18,Ffor compensation four years after the
OL,19,Fevent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
