PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779905470
OL,3,C'Absolute turmoil': Liverpool fan
OL,4,Crebuilding life after attack at Paris
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FHe has one more year of training
OL,8,Fbefore he becomes a qualified
OL,9,Fpsychotherapist- supported by friends
OL,10,Fand fundraisers.
OL,12,FThe 51-year-old is now set to complete
OL,13,Fa placement with the Hillsborough
OL,14,FSurvivors Alliance, who also provide
OL,15,Ftherapy for survivors of Paris and
OL,16,FHillsborough.
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
